    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing a rare find for even the most discerning buyer. Every aspect of the car has been meticulously preserved, from the flawless exterior paint and pristine interior upholstery to the engine bay, which remains in showroom-quality state. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory\u2014the engine is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features and climate controls function perfectly. There are no leaks, no odd noises, and no signs of wear. This is an investment-grade vehicle that offers a like-new driving experience and requires absolutely no additional work.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant rust patches and several large dents. The interior shows heavy wear, including tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronic components. The engine requires major repairs to be reliably drivable.",
      "price": 5500.0,
